            {
              "title": "Placement & Combining Tips",
              "content": "Prerequisite: Level 2. Students just beginning Latin should start at Level 1 and consider the optional online course.\n\nNOTE: for Levels 3-4, students work through materials at their own pace, and lesson plans are not provided. This course may be counted as 1 credit for High School."
